## 레이어별 최소 코드 구조

### Controller 최소 구조
```java
@Controller
public class XxxController extends BaseController {
    @Autowired XxxServiceImpl xxxService;

    @RequestMapping(value = "/domain/sub/xxxList.do")
    public String xxxList(@ModelAttribute("searchVO") XxxVO searchVO, Model model) throws Exception {
        return "/domain/sub/xxxList." + searchVO.getLayout();
    }
}
```

### ServiceImpl 최소 구조
```java
@Service
public class XxxServiceImpl extends EgovAbstractServiceImpl {
    @Resource private XxxDAO xxxDAO;
}
```

### DAO 최소 구조
```java
@Repository
public class XxxDAO extends EgovComAbstractDAO {
}
```

### VO 최소 구조
```java
@Setter @Getter
public class XxxVO extends CommonVO {
    private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;
}
```

### XML mapper 최소 구조
```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE mapper PUBLIC "-//mybatis.org//DTD Mapper 3.0//EN" "http://mybatis.org/dtd/mybatis-3-mapper.dtd">
<mapper namespace="domain.feature.xxx">
</mapper>
```
